<chapter condition="TITLE=System Features: Parameter Maintenance;ACCESS=BA_PARAM"
         role="TOPIC">
  <title>Parameter Maintenance</title>

  <section condition="TITLE=System Features: Parameter Maintenance" id="BPM"
           role="TOPIC">
    <title>Parameter Maintenance</title>

    <para role="TEXT">A bank administrator can define standard parameters for
    Financial Holidays and Financial Cutoff Times for different products and
    Product types within the <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml"
    xpointer="ent_appli" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/>.</para>

    <para role="TEXT">Selecting this function will display a parameter Type
    field to select either Financial Holidays and Financial Cutoff Times.
    Click the select button after the choice is made, to display a list of
    defined parameters.</para>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Parameter Maintenance - Navigation</title>

      <para role="TEXT">To navigate to the <emphasis role="bold">Parameter
      Maintenance</emphasis> function, from the toolbar, select
      <emphasis>System Features</emphasis> from the home page, then select
      <emphasis>Parameter Maintenance</emphasis> from the left side navigation
      menu.</para>
    </section>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Parameter Maintenance - Selection</title>

      <para role="TEXT">Selecting this function will display a parameter Type
      field to select either Financial Holidays and Financial Cutoff Times,
      from a drop down menu.</para>

      <para role="TEXT">Click the select button after the choice is made, to
      display a list of defined parameters.</para>
    </section>

    <section condition="TITLE=Parameter Maintenance: Financial Holidays Parameter List; ACCESS=BPM_01"
             id="BPM_New" role="ITEM">
